{"tid":2177106,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"柳俊江質疑：參與暴動會報警？","createTime":"2020-08-27T13:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T13:18:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eb541134b0784973d375fe8507ff900732887be4","tid":2177106,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T13:18:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/FMQYJNOAGJAU5MRCI2GIXV2PEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FFMQYJNOAGJAU5MRCI2GIXV2PEQ%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=6939e6f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FFMQYJNOAGJAU5MRCI2GIXV2PEQ%2F&h=3a39e417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/FMQYJNOAGJAU5MRCI2GIXV2PEQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江質疑：參與暴動會報警？<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】林卓廷突然由「原告變被告」，引起全城譁然。去年7.21當晚在元朗現場遇襲受傷的傳媒人柳俊江昨日形容警方的行徑「完全超越指鹿為馬嘅典故」，指林卓廷若參與暴動，為何會主動報警。他批評警方已淪為政權圓滿政治操作的機器，又指被捕不可怕，因為「最可怕係香港某部份人嘅集體精神失常」。<br />\n<br />\n訪問逾40位7.21事件當事人寫成《元朗黑夜》一書的傳媒人柳俊江昨在facebook披露書中紀錄，指當晚約10時半，林卓廷從網上影片得知元朗雞地有大批白衣人襲擊市民，隨即致電元朗警民關係組姓鄧警長，並乘坐港鐵到。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dqV_UnkUVtNMY7RUNYLw31rVeLU=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MMRDBEGNCVCO7L3F54KL5KD2ZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdqV_UnkUVtNMY7RUNYLw31rVeLU%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMMRDBEGNCVCO7L3F54KL5KD2ZU.jpg&h=edd59081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年7.21在元朗站遇襲血流披面的傳媒人柳俊江，昨在節目上炮轟警方執法不公。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「政治操作有眼睇」<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷當晚在元朗站向市民指閘外有黑社會集結，呼籲不要出閘，其間有列車到站，當時閘內有過百名男女老少不知所措，收費閘外白衣人再度聚集，並向閘內市民發動攻擊，雙。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江提出四項疑問，林卓廷身為立法會議員，到場履行監察責任，到底如何破壞社會安寧？若林卓廷要破壞社會安寧，為何到場前後都主動報警？警方如指控林卓廷參與暴動，是否。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江在本報節目上轟警方執法不公，昨日十多人涉暴動被捕，料很快便會提上法庭，對比起不少白衣人仍逍遙法外，指政治操作人人「有眼睇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fpn2gujZHM0akWkuyhLwQSUvwy4=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BNVUZFXYMZFHDP3NF3P4MFOEP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffpn2gujZHM0akWkuyhLwQSUvwy4%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBNVUZFXYMZFHDP3NF3P4MFOEP4.jpg&h=3808753d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柳俊江"}]}